divs: Sighting Detailsi just wrote to you guys a couple hours ago and after searching youtube for a little i saw that on the west coast there were multiple sightings of unidentified lights in the sky... THE FLASHING LIGHT IN THOSE VIDEOS IS WHAT I SAW HERE ON THE EAST COAST!!! that somewhat gave me the closure i needed but maybe that is also a giant breakthrough for you guys... PLEASE LOOK INTO THIS! i know that whatever it is its something really deep cause thats the same thing i saw here in jersey...
